title: Voyetra AudioStation 32 & MIDI Orchestrator 32
description:
Voyetra AudioStation 32/MIDI Orchestrator 32
circa 1998

Ripped from:
DELL-Voyetra Turtle Beach 64 Voice Montego II
Windows95/98/NT, Drivers/Applications (V4.05)

Yes, this came from DELL; it looks just like the retail Voyetra.

It installed just fine on my Toshiba Satellite under XP SP3 (my 
old Toshi will never have a clue about quality audio card!).

The apps look just like what is pictured on this page:
 <a href="
http://www.dearhoney.idv.tw/soundcard/vortex2/montegoiiplus.htm" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://www.dearhoney.idv.tw/soundcard/vortex2/montegoiiplus.htm</a>

(if the page is gone by the time you get this, I've included a 
copy in the torrent).

The package includes the following apps:

Program				Version
MIDI Orchestrator 32(tm) 	1.3.0.18
AudioView 32 (TM) 		1.1.0.13
AudioStation 32 (TM) 		1.1.0.57
Voyetra System Tray  		1.2.0.1
SoundCheck (TM)  		2.1.0.10
SoundCheck Mixer (TM)  		1.1.0.5

Voyetra formed a close alliance with Dell in the 90s. That means 
most Voyetra/Turtle Beach apps can be found in some Dell branded 
machine.

IF you are looking for more Dell packages, just go here: <a href="
ftp://ftp.us.dell.com/audio/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
ftp://ftp.us.dell.com/audio/</a>
